headline: UnitedHealth Group (UNH) Q2 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: UnitedHealth (UNH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -15.70% and +0.06%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
